sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant UI as machine-ui
    participant BC as BuyController
    participant Om as OmisePaymentService
    participant Inv as InventoryService

    rect rgb(240,248,255)
        Note over UI,Inv: ยกเลิก — POST /api/buy/cancel
        UI->>BC: cancel(charge_id)
        alt charge_id ไม่ใช่ draft_*
            BC->>Om: cancel_charge(charge_id)
        end
        BC->>Inv: cancel_order (เฉพาะ pending_payment)
        Inv-->>BC: ok / fail
        BC-->>UI: cancelled หรือ 409
    end

    rect rgb(255,248,240)
        Note over UI,Inv: Dev — POST /api/buy/mock-pay
        UI->>BC: mock_pay(charge_id)
        BC->>BC: order_statuses = paid
        BC->>BC: _execute_dispense(charge_id)
        BC-->>UI: paid + dispense result message
    end
